President Muhammadu Buhari on Saturday received the second jab of the AstraZeneca vaccine against COVID-19 in the Presidential Villa in Abuja. Dr Sanusi Rafindadi administered the jab on President Buhari, who was dressed in an all-white attire. The President, alongside the Vice President, Professor Yemi Osinbajo (SAN), had in March, received the first jab during a ceremony at the Banquet Hall of the State House. Details Laterâ€¦